        "formTitle": "Nightly Shift Logbook",
        "formDescription": "Complete this form at the end of your shift. For Sales Intervals: AM shift = Open–11am / 11am–1pm / 1pm–Close. PM shift = 5pm–7pm / 7pm–9pm / 9pm–Close.",
